title: Triple Chocolate Truffle Ice Cream - 16oz - Favorite Day™
Decription:
Triple Chocolate Truffle Ice Cream from Favorite Day™ makes for an irresistibly delicious treat to enjoy whenever your sweet tooth is calling. This frozen treat features a delectable, creamy base of dark chocolate ice cream, taken up a notch with fudge, dark fudge truffles and chocolate flakes for a scrumptious chocolate flavored medley that'll have you grinning from ear to ear. The pint-sized ice cream is perfect for enjoying several servings — on your own or with a friend! — and it's made with real milk and cream for that rich, chocolaty flavor you crave. Great on its own, triple chocolate truffle ice cream also makes a tasty accompaniment to a fresh-out-of-the-oven chocolate chip cookie for the perfect combination of warm and cool delight. You can even enjoy a spoonful or two in a waffle or sugar cone topped with extra fudge bits, sprinkles and other ice cream fixings for a heavenly dessert.

A little bliss in every bite. Guaranteed to be a favorite or your money back.

title: Addison Rattan Floor Lamp Natural - Threshold™
description: Add natural style to your interiors with the Addison Rattan Floor Lamp from Threshold™. This freestanding floor lamp base makes a great addition to your everyday lighting. It features a downward-facing dome-shaped rattan shade for a natural look and a curved metal body with a pedestal base in a sleek black finish. This floor lamp comes with a simple on/off switch for effortless illumination. Place it next to a sofa in your living room or lounge room for endless display potential around your home.
